'''Artom's Crest''' was the highest rock spire rising from the molten surface of [[Rennokk]], a [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]], rising more than 20,000 [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]]. [[Reidi Artom]] landed here while conducting her survey of the [[Cularin system/Legends|Cularin system]]. It was the only named location on Rennokk.

